show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/2kxSWP
show.description: Lara Khuraana faces the worst day of her life when her parents give her an ultimatum to marry, she loses her job and her boyfriend leaves her for another girl. She then meets a dashing billionaire with hidden identity, who wants her to donate bone marrow for his brother’s life. In exchange for helping him, Lara demands a fake marriage with Rahul Saxena. They both live in the same house and slowly start liking each other. Rahul secretly helps Lara with her job interviews. She soon finds out that Rahul is a successful businessman and just when everything seems fine, Rahul’s lover and ex-fiancee creates a scene. Because of her interference, Rahul and Lara break apart for a while but soon, Rahul goes public and announces that he wants Lara back in his life. She returns to him and they marry each other in front of their families.
